{
  "topology_id": "TOPO-NETRA-REF-001",
  "title": "NETRA reference SD-WAN-over-MPLS topology (5 sites, ~20 nodes)",
  "description": "Five-site enterprise: a datacenter (dual PE + RR), a hub, three branches, and an MPLS provider core (IS-IS + SR-MPLS). L3VPN VRFs CORP (RD/RT 100:1) and OT (RD/RT 100:2). Overlay is strongSwan GRE-over-IPSec hub-spoke + partial mesh. This is the authoritative topology graph for GraphRAG-lite blast-radius reasoning.",
